      <h3>Signing the declaration</h3>
      <p>The declaration for a new application must be signed by either a business owner or a director.</p>
      <p>They can do this online through GOV.UK Verify, or they <a href="">can print the declaration</a>, sign it and return it to the <a href="">Central Licensing Office</a>.</p>
      <p>Only UK residents with valid passports can use GOV.UK Verify.</p>
      <hr />
      <fieldset>
        <fieldset>
          <legend><b>How would you like to sign the declaration?</b></legend>
          <div class="field checkbox">
            <label><input type="radio" name="declarations" value="verify">use GOV.UK Verify</label>
          </div>
          <div class="field checkbox">
            <label><input type="radio" name="declarations" value="post">print, sign and return</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>
      </fieldset>
  
      <div class="js-verify">
        <h3 class="important">Important</h3>
        <p>By applying I agree to follow the rules below, and I’m aware that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>the rules will be recorded on my licence</li>
          <li>my licence could be revoked, suspended or curtailed if I don’t follow them </li>
          <li>it’s a criminal offence not to follow the rules</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="steps">
          <h4>Laws</h4>
          <p>I agree to obey laws that cover:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>operating vehicles</li>
            <li>drivers’ hours</li>
            <li>tachographs</li>
            <li>speed limits</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Passengers</h4>
          <p>I won’t carry more passengers in my vehicles than I’m allowed to.</p>
          <h4>Records</h4>
          <p>I’ll maintain proper records and show them when they’re needed.</p>
          <p>I’ll also:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>keep records of driver reports for 15 months</li>
            <li>record defects, safety inspections, maintenance and repairs</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Vehicle conditions</h4>
          <p>I’ll keep my vehicles in good condition, and:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>promptly report any defects, or symptoms of them</li>
            <li>record the details in writing</li>
            <li>show records when they’re needed</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Informing the Traffic Commissioner</h4>
          <p>I’ll tell the Traffic Commissioner within 28 days if:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>there are any other changes that might affect the licence</li>
            <li>anyone mentioned in this application is convicted of an offence</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Declaration</h4>
          <p>I declare that:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>the statements I’ve made in this application are true</li>
            <li>all supporting evidence is correct</li>
            <li>I understand that it’s an offence to make a false declaration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="field confirm">
          <label>
            <input type="checkbox">
            I declare that the statements made in this application are true and that all supporting evidence supplied with regard to my application is correct. I understand that it is an offence to make a false declaration.
          </label>
        </div>
